text: Robert Osborne (4 February 1897 - 21 February 1975) was an Australian cricketer. He played three first-class matches for New South Wales between 1924/25 and 1926/27. ==See also== * List of New South Wales representative cricketers ==References== ==External links== * Category:1897 births Category:1975 deaths Category:Australian cricketers Category:New South Wales cricketers Category:Cricketers from Sydney
title: Robert Osborne (New South Wales cricketer)
